<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pay-lip-service-to">pay lip service (to)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对…空口答应 (而不行动)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Should we just pay lip service or take practical measures to protect the environment?  
我们应该仅仅只是说说而已还是应该采取实际行动去保护环境呢？</p><footer>2013 江苏改</footer></div></div>